[05/12/2017 20:09:53] <font color="#ffffff">Un primate nocturno.</font>
[05/12/2017 20:09:57] <font color="#ffffff">Un oso mutante come hormigas.</font>
[05/12/2017 20:10:02] <font color="#ffffff">Una gigantesca rana púrpura</font>
